TITLE: Episode 131 - Desist, Detox, Detrans with Cat Cattinson [Adult Language]
DESCRIPTION: This week, we are joined by the wonderful Cat Cattinson. Once trans, Cat is a student of biology who decided to desist and detransition back to her natural femininity. The transgender activists would have you believe that medical gender transition is a universal good for those with gender dysphoria and that no one ever regrets their decision to transition. Cat disagrees. So, let's talk about that.
